68
00:04:45,200 --> 00:04:46,530
What a relief...

69
00:04:47,580 --> 00:04:50,200
K-Kickzaw!

70
00:05:04,730 --> 00:05:05,720
Safe...

71
00:05:06,980 --> 00:05:08,350
D-Damn it!

72
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:10,480
Hijikata!

73
00:05:10,900 --> 00:05:12,320
You've finally showed your true colors!

74
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:17,230
Sogo Okita, Captain of the 1st Division, shall purge you as a traitor!

75
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:27,180
I-It'd be dangerous if the dog swallowed it.

76
00:05:27,860 --> 00:05:29,500
Okay, now it's safe.

77
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:33,540
Wh-What are you doing?!

78
00:05:33,850 --> 00:05:39,890
["When breaking a Chuubert in half, the end with the knob should be better. It's also tasty to drink from there."]

79
00:05:57,490 --> 00:05:59,270
W-Water...

80
